# ── Required ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Your club's main Google Sheet (17 tabs, see README for structure)
VITE_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID=your_google_sheet_id_here
VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_api_key_here

# ── Optional: RIB Booking ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Separate Google Sheet for daily RIB scheduling.
# Tab name must be: "RIB BOKNING <year>" (e.g. "RIB BOKNING 2026")
# Enables RIB Booking tab in Fleet page + widget on Dashboard.
# VITE_RIB_BOOKING_SHEET_ID=your_rib_booking_sheet_id_here

# ── Optional: Coach Time Tracking ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Separate Google Sheet where coaches log hours.
# Tab name must be: "<year>" (e.g. "2026")
# Enables Time Log tab in Coaches & Team page.
# VITE_COACH_TIME_SHEET_ID=your_coach_time_sheet_id_here

# ── Notes ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# All club config (name, coordinates, social links, feature flags, pricing) is
# read from the "Settings" tab in the main Google Sheet — not from env vars.
# See src/config/clubConfig.ts for the full list of setting keys and defaults.
#
# If VITE_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID or VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY is missing, the app falls back
# to built-in sample data automatically.
